Interface Observer<K,V>

All Known Subinterfaces:
EvictObserver<K,V>, GetObserver<K,V>, PutObserver<K,V>, RemoveObserver<K,V>
public interface Observer<K,V>

This interface is only an abstract interface for GetObserver and PutObserver. You should either implement GetObserver, PutObserver or both. But you should not directly implement the Observer.
